No.	ISO 27001 Control 	Applicable (Yes/No)	Justification
1	Information Classification	Yes	"We classified assets as Public, Internal, Confidential."
2	Access Control	Yes	"Prevent unauthorized access to HR, Payroll, Customer Database, etc."
3	Identity Management	Yes	Manage user accounts throughout their lifecycle.
4	Authentication Information (Passwords & MFA)	Yes	"Strong authentication, including passwords and MFA, is required to verify user identities and reduce the risk of unauthorized access to critical systems."
5	Privileged Access Rights	Yes	Control administrator accounts.
6	Information Backup	Yes	Protect against backup failure and accidental deletion.
7	Malware Protection	Yes	Protect employee laptops from malware.
8	Vulnerability Management	Yes	Reduce vulnerabilities through patching.
9	Secure Configuration	Yes	"Secure AWS, Wi-Fi Router, Microsoft 365."
10	Logging & Monitoring	Yes	Detect suspicious activities.
11	Cryptography	Yes	Protect Customer Database and Payroll Data.
12	Information Security Awareness	Yes	Reduce phishing and human errors.
13	Incident Management	Yes	Handle security incidents effectively.
14	Supplier Security	Yes	Protect vendor relationships and contracts.
15	Physical Security	Yes	Protect office equipment and networking devices.
16	Secure Development 	Yes	Protect source code and development activities.
17	Business Continuity / ICT Readiness	Yes	Ensure recovery after major disruptions.
